title: War of the Roses: Words With Friends
description: Erin met someone randomly through playing Words with Friends.  They started talking and it boiled into a romantic relationship.  The problem, they've never seen each other in person and the only time he's tried to make plans to meet, has been when he's on a business trip.  So now Erin is wondering if he is who he says he is, or if he's hiding a family from her?
